---

# Setup Instructions

## 1. Backend Setup

```bash
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
```

Backend runs on:

```text
http://127.0.0.1:5000
```

---

## 2. Frontend Setup

Open a new terminal:

```bash
cd frontend
python -m http.server 8000
```

Frontend runs on:

```text
http://localhost:8000
```

---

# Database

- SQLite database is used
- Database is created automatically on first run
- All application data is stored persistently

---

# Notes

- No UI modifications were made as per assessment instructions
- All features are fully functional
- Each admin can only access their own opportunities
- Backend APIs are properly secured and validated
